@startuml as
title Prompting Sequencer State (GoalMeetingPanel)

[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Preparing : run()
Preparing --> Planning : registry + prompts ready
Planning --> BuildQueue : plan parsed
BuildQueue --> StepExecuting : workQueue exists
StepExecuting --> StepExecuting : next step
StepExecuting --> CascadeExecuting : after steps
CascadeExecuting --> Completed : all ok
StepExecuting --> Failed : step non-zero / hard error
CascadeExecuting --> Failed : cascade failed or overflow
Planning --> Failed : planning failed
Preparing --> Failed : environment/setup failed
Completed --> Idle
Failed --> Idle

@enduml
